Map by kan3 - Relatively interesting fun yard map where the CT must take out the camping T. Some features of the map include
1.) no traditional buyzones
2.) Placed weapons and functional "ammo crates"
3.) Anti camp and anti AFK system
4.) Built in pseudo "time limit" to speed up gameplay
5.) Overlay instructions to help keep new players informed...can be read on medium and high texture resolution setting
6.) Some custom bumpmap textures for looks department
7.) Supports 40 players
